The paper discusses the concept of physical-layer security and its application in 5G wireless systems, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the integration of multiple services into one transmission, which is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of artificial noise, which is a technique used in multimedia (cs.MM) and system and control (cs.SY).
